Class GZipFileManager

java.lang.Object
com.ibm.dtfj.utils.file.FileManager
com.ibm.dtfj.utils.file.SimpleFileManager
com.ibm.dtfj.utils.file.CompressedFileManager
com.ibm.dtfj.utils.file.GZipFileManager
public class GZipFileManager extends CompressedFileManager
File manger for gzip'd files. The gzip algorithm does not support a hierarchical archive and only works on a single file.
